data.description: Motivated Seller will pay up to $5,000 of closing costs!!Welcome to this inviting 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse that offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience and technology.As you approach, you'll notice the spacious covered patio. A perfect spot to enjoy your morning cup of coffee or relax in the evening.Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. This design creates an ideal space for entertaining family and friends. The living room is bathed in natural light, making it a welcoming spot to unwind after a long day. The kitchen, with stainless steel appliances, island, pantry and ample storage. Also, on the main level is a half bath.Upstairs you will find the 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms which includes the primary bedroom and en-suite bathroom with double sinks. The remaining bedrooms offer plenty of space with a jack and jill bathroom with double sinks. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs with the bedrooms.For the tech-savvy homeowner, this townhouse comes equipped with smart home features. You can control the lighting, water, appliances and more with just a few taps on your smartphone or voice commands. It's the perfect fusion of modern convenience and cutting-edge technology.Outside you will find a nice sized shed to store your lawn equipment, a patio for grilling and ample space for the kids to play. The heated 2 stall garage, with shelving, will keep your vehicles nice and warm this winter.In summary, this 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom townhouse with a two-stall heated garage offers a contemporary and convenient lifestyle. With its open floor plan, laundry on the same floor as the bedrooms, and smart home features, it's designed to make daily living a breeze while providing you with the utmost comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhouse your new home!
